definition: to bear/to carry/to hold/to continue/to undertake/to take charge/owing to/due to/to receive
surname Cheng/Cheng (c. 2000 BC), third of the legendary Flame Emperors 炎帝[Yan2 di4] descended from Shennong 神農|神农[Shen2 nong2] Farmer God
to carry/to convey/to load/to hold/to fill up/and/also/as well as/simultaneously
to record in writing/to carry (i.e. publish in a newspaper etc)/Taiwan pr. [zai4]/year

sentences.english: A new table of axial capacity parameter of driven pile has been compiled.
sentences.chinese: 在此基础上编制了新的打入桩竖向承载力参数表。

sentences.english: Influence of loading path on axial strength of circular tubular TX-joints.
sentences.chinese: 荷载路径对TX型圆管节点轴向承载力的影响。

sentences.english: The paper is accompanied with a self-developed software called LandSmart that is for facilitating calculating land demand and land-population sustainability.
sentences.chinese: 并自主设计出土地需求量和土地人口承载力预测软件。

sentences.english: The bearing capacity of the cold-formed thin-walled steel which was used in combination wall.
sentences.chinese: 分析了冷弯薄壁型钢在组合墙体中的承载力。

sentences.english: Method of capacity of socketed piles are determined to bring together.
sentences.chinese: 归纳总结了确定嵌岩灌注桩的承载力方法。

sentences.english: The calculation of land potential capacity is the basis ofthe research of land population supporting capacity.
sentences.chinese: 土地生产潜力的计算是研究土地人口承载力的基础。

sentences.english: Analysis on static wind response and ultimate carrying capacity of long-span roofs.
sentences.chinese: 大跨度屋盖结构的静风效应及静风极限承载力分析。

sentences.english: The proposed method is applied to assess the water resources carrying capacity of Rizhao region.
sentences.chinese: 最后将该方法应用于日照市水资源承载力的评价中。

sentences.english: The Formula of ultimate flexural capacity is given according to Plastic Principle.
sentences.chinese: 通过塑性铰理论，推导了加固后梁的承载力计算公式。

sentences.english: The test research of shear strength of steel reinforced super-high-strength concrete short columns is carried out.
sentences.chinese: 研究了钢骨超高强混凝土框架短柱的抗剪承载力。

sentences.english: Conic roller bearing is used for desirable bearing capacity.
sentences.chinese: 园锥滚柱轴承，承载力大。

sentences.english: Furthermore, the contribution of flanges to the shear resistance of the wall was analysed.
sentences.chinese: 同时还分析了翼缘对墙片的抗剪承载力的贡献。

sentences.english: This paper puts forward a calculation method for section steel concrete pillar.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一种型钢混凝土柱正截面承载力计算方法。

sentences.english: The collapsibility loess with lower bearing capacity is liable to yield the settlement deformation.
sentences.chinese: 湿陷性黄土易产生沉降变形，且承载力低。

sentences.english: As the world’s population continues to boom so does density in major conurbations.
sentences.chinese: 随着世界人口的激增，大城市的承载力也在猛增。

sentences.english: Estimated the bearing capacity of foundation with multi-parameter.
sentences.chinese: 多参数神经网络综合预估地基的承载力。

definition: to sustain/to bear the weight (of the upper storeys in architecture)/load-bearing
to support/to bear the weight of (a building)
